Class LinePosition

  • java.lang.Object
    • LinePosition

  • public class LinePosition
extends java.lang.Object
    LinePosition class defines a LinePosition object. Creates a LinePosition object given an int line number and word position. LinePosition is stored within a Linear Linked List in a Word Object.
    Version:
    5/17/2019
    Author:
    Joshua Matson
